                    <span>2013-04-15</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">本来以为只是一本流于形式的普通畅销书，结果还算好读。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="835155960">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-835155960" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-835155960" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="835155960">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yuxiaomiao/">喵</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2014-08-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">玄乎极了，而且跟其他的书重复太多。基本上武志红就那么些料了。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="940153611">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-940153611" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-940153611" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="940153611">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/amelieho/">小默</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-07-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这本书读到后面好累。难怪不少人书评觉得玄，因为实在是塞了太多东西在一起，有些内容级别还很高（所以不是完全看懂）。这么多方法放到一起讨论当然可以说是人心的道理殊途同归，可是要消化确实辛苦。能这样简单明了的写出来，作者也很是厉害。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="628615555">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-628615555" class="vote-count">38</span>
