  <div class="hd">
    <h2>
      读书笔记&nbsp;&nbsp;· · · · · ·&nbsp;
          <span class="pl">(<a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/20475794/annotation">共<span property="v:count">237</span>篇</a>)</span>

    </h2>

      <a class="redbutt rr j a_show_login" href="https://www.douban.com/register?reason=annotate" rel="nofollow"><span>我来写笔记</span></a>
  </div>
  

    <div class="bd">
      <ul class="inline-tabs">
        <li class="on"><a href="#rank" id="by_rank" >按有用程度</a></li>
        <li><a href="#page" id="by_page" >按页码先后</a></li>
        <li><a href="#time" id="by_time" >最新笔记</a></li>
      </ul>
      
  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="23898264">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3774094/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3774094-2.jpg" alt="寻舟流火霜肇通" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23898264/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23898264/" class="">第29页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3774094/" class=" " title="寻舟流火霜肇通">寻舟流火霜肇通</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="23898264">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">在遇到焦虑和挑战的时候，我们很容易难受，把注意力放在外面，试图抓住一些别的东西，希望这些外在资源能帮助自己去面对暂时似乎超出自己能力的挑战。越这样越容易失控的原因是：外在的无法被掌控，反而会增加焦虑。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23898264/">(<span class="">3回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-01-14 22:37</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">8人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                在遇到焦虑和挑战的时候，我们很容易难受，把注意力放在外面，试图抓住一些别的东西，希望这些外在资源能帮助自己去面对暂时似乎超出自己能力的挑战。越这样越容易失控的原因是：外在的无法被掌控，反而会增加焦虑。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

